connection to the box which can  support as many as three
parallel ports and one "Uniport" that can be  configured
as either parallel or serial (NETPrint/150).  The
"Uniport"  requires a $60 adapter for use as a parallel
printer port. The NETPrint/100  supports one parallel
port and one RJ45 "Uniport."  The JETPrint/100/150 
